template:
{{if .visual_result}}
{{if eq .visual_result "pass"}}
### ✅ Visual Sample Inspection Passed

The visual inspection of the consignment sample has been completed successfully.

* **Sample Number**: `{{.sample_number}}`
* **Result**: 🟢 Pass — No pests or damage detected
{{if .visual_comments}}* **Inspector Notes**: {{.visual_comments}}{{end}}
{{else if eq .visual_result "fail"}}
### 🔴 Visual Sample Inspection Failed

The visual inspection of the sample detected pests or damage. The consignment cannot proceed for a phytosanitary certificate.

* **Sample Number**: `{{.sample_number}}`
* **Result**: 🔴 Fail — Infestation or damage detected
{{if .visual_comments}}* **Inspector Notes**: {{.visual_comments}}{{end}}
{{else if eq .visual_result "escalate_consignment"}}
### ⚠️ Escalated to Consignment Inspection

The PQS officer has determined that the sample inspection is insufficient and has requested a full consignment inspection.

* **Sample Number**: `{{.sample_number}}`
* **Reason**: Sample deemed insufficient — consignment inspection required
{{if .visual_comments}}* **Inspector Notes**: {{.visual_comments}}{{end}}

You will be contacted to schedule the consignment inspection.
{{end}}
{{else}}
### ⏳ Visual Sample Inspection in Progress

The PQS officer is conducting a visual inspection of the consignment sample.

* **Sample Number**: `{{.sample_number}}`
* **Reference Number**: `{{.reference_number}}`

No action is required at this stage. You will be notified once the results are available.
{{end}}
